      • isClass

        boolean isClass()
        Returns:
        true if the container is a class, false if it is a package
        See Also:
        isPackage()

      • isPackage

        boolean isPackage()
        Returns:
        true if the container is a package, false if it is a class.
        See Also:
        isClass()

      • parentContainer

        IJClassContainer<?> parentContainer()
        Returns:
        Parent IJClassContainer. If this is a package, this method returns a parent package, or null if this package is the root package. If this is an outer-most class, this method returns a JPackage to which it belongs. If this is an inner class, this method returns the outer class.

      • getPackage

        JPackage getPackage()
        Returns:
        The nearest package parent. If this.isPackage(), then return this.
